  "dct_description_sm": [
    "New York Metro-North Railroad Stations - West of Hudson River, 2009 is a point theme representing stations on the Metro-North Railroad Port Jervis and Pascack Valley Lines. Attribute data includes the names of the lines, names of the stations and operating agency. Raw data was acquired from files from the New York State Department of Transportation. Data is provided in the projection NAD83 to align with the NYCMap basemap. The realigned data has not been thoroughly checked for accuracy."
